.head 4 -  Description: Changes the IsValidNumber( ) so that any user input between min
max ranges is valid and doesnt need to be a multiple of nIncrement
.head 4 +  Derived From 
.head 5 -  Class: cSpinField
.head 4 -  Class Variables 
.head 4 +  Instance Variables 
.head 5 -  Number: nMinValue
.head 5 -  Number: nMaxValue
.head 5 -  Number: nIncrement
.head 5 -  Number: nAdjust
.head 5 -  Number: nInitialValue
.head 5 -  Boolean: bEditable
.head 4 +  Functions 
.head 5 +  Function: IsValidNumber
.head 6 -  Description: Same as IsValidNumber except doesnt return false if the
number is not a multiple of nIncrement.
.head 6 +  Returns 
.head 7 -  Boolean: 
.head 6 -  Parameters 
.head 6 -  Static Variables 
.head 6 +  Local variables 
.head 7 -  String: sValue
.head 7 -  Number: nValue
.head 6 +  Actions 
.head 7 -  Set sValue = GetNumber()
.head 7 -  !
.head 7 -  ! ***** Validate for valid number
.head 7 +  If Not SalStrIsValidNumber( sValue )
.head 8 -  Return FALSE
.head 7 -  !
.head 7 -  ! ***** Test if value is on an increment
.head 7 +  If nAdjust
.head 8 -  Set nValue = SalStrToNumber( sValue ) / SalNumberPower( 10, nAdjust )
.head 7 +  Else 
.head 8 -  Set nValue = SalStrToNumber( sValue )
.head 7 -  !
.head 7 -  ! ***** Test if value out of range
.head 7 +  If nValue < nMinValue or nValue > nMaxValue
.head 8 -  Return FALSE
.head 7 -  !
.head 7 -  Return TRUE
.head 4 +  Message Actions 
.head 5 +  On SAM_Create
.head 6 -  Set nMinValue = 0
.head 6 -  Set nMaxValue = 10
.head 6 -  Set nIncrement = 1
.head 6 -  Set nAdjust = 0
.head 6 -  Set nInitialValue = 0
.head 6 -  Set bEditable = TRUE
.head 6 -  Call SalSendMsg( hWndItem, PAM_cls_SETINSTANCEVARS, 0, 0 )
.head 6 -  Call SetNumberProperties( nMinValue, nMaxValue, nIncrement, nAdjust )
.head 6 -  Call SetNumber( nInitialValue )
.head 6 +  If bEditable
.head 7 -  Call SalSendMsg( hWndItem, PAM_clsSPN_ENABLE, 0, 0 )
.head 6 +  Else 
.head 7 -  Call SalSendMsg( hWndItem, PAM_clsSPN_DISABLE, 0, 0 )
.head 5 +  On PAM_clsSPN_DISABLE
.head 6 -  Call SalDisableWindow( hWndItem )
.head 6 -  Return TRUE
.head 5 +  On PAM_clsSPN_ENABLE
.head 6 -  Call SalEnableWindow( hWndItem )
.head 6 -  Return TRUE
.head 5 +  On PAM_clsSPN_SHOW
.head 6 -  Call SalShowWindow( hWndItem )
.head 6 -  Return TRUE
.head 5 +  On PAM_clsSPN_HIDE
.head 6 -  Call SalHideWindow( hWndItem )
.head 6 -  Return TRUE
